be </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">unlikely to </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">find suitably sized </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">private sector</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> accommodation </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">in England</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> within the cap</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">.</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> </span></li></ol><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="10" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">We have developed a “robust” approach to engagement with households that find themselves in this situation.  </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">A dedicated Housing Welfare </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">R</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">eform Team</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> (HWRT) </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">operates within the multi-agency team looking at solutions for households faced with having to move.</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">  The team operates a </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">two stage interview setting out the </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">housing options at the first session, followed up by a </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">thorough assessment of the</span><span style="font-