p</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">rovided to meet the benefit shortfall.  The claimant found work in July 2013. </span></li></ul><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 54pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 54pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Quote from c</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">laimant </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">about their experience: </span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 54pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 54pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">“It was good that they contacted me to offer help. I didn’t know that the council would be able to help me with it or that the </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">jobcentre would be involved too. Childcare, rent and travel for the first month was a big worry so it was a great that I could go to the council and get it all sorted under one roof. “</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 54pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ul type="square" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Wingdings; font-size:12pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 46.49pt; padding-left:7.51pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Lone parent with three children who had last worked in 2001. Action pl</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">an agreed with claimant to actively seek employment and DHP agreed to cover </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">the benefit shortfall. The claimant found work </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">with </span><a name="_GoBack"></a><span style="font-family:'Times New 